cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.NE 

The paper presents a novel reinforcement learning method for continuous state and action spaces, which is likely to fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), systems and control (cs.SY), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The paper focuses on developing a new RL method for solving linearly-solvable Markov decision processes (L-MDPs) without active exploration, which is a problem commonly encountered in robotics and control systems. Therefore, the paper is likely to be relevant to these sub-categories.
